---
description: When a VOM ticket is in state review-pending, use the verifier subagent for implementation review.
alwaysApply: true
---

When you are working on a VOM ticket and its state is **review-pending**, invoke the **verifier** subagent with that ticket ID (e.g. `/verifier TKT-010`). Do not review and approve the implementation in the same flow; let the verifier run the workflow and report back.
